# Change Log - Iteration 2

## Feature 1: Save Conversation History (Story Points: 4)
- **Description**: Automatically save user prompts and LLM responses with timestamps
- **Implementation**: Added database schema and auto-save on each message exchange
- **PR Links**: [To be added after development]
- **Status**: Completed

## Feature 2: View Conversation History (Story Points: 3)
- **Description**: Users can view all past conversations in a dedicated history page
- **Implementation**: Created `/history` page that displays all saved conversations
- **PR Links**: [To be added after development]
- **Status**: Completed

## Feature 3: Search Conversation History (Story Points: 5)
- **Description**: Search through conversations using keywords
- **Implementation**: Added search functionality to filter conversations by content
- **PR Links**: [To be added after development]
